Package: vvnthemes
Title: Visualizing Virginia's Numbers Themes and Templates
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    person("Visualizing Virginia's Numbers", "Virginia Tech",
           email = "vvn@vt.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides ggplot2 themes, color palettes, scales, GT table styles,
    Leaflet map helpers, Shiny UI components, and ready-to-use Quarto / Shiny
    project templates for the Visualizing Virginia's Numbers (VVN) at Virginia
    Tech. Inspired by urbnthemes. All outputs follow VT brand guidelines
    (Maroon #861F41, Orange #E5751F) and meet WCAG 2.1 AA accessibility
    requirements.
